<item>
            <title>[LU-3367] Interop 2.1.5&lt;-&gt;2.4 failure on test suite lfsck: remove_ost_objects: command not found</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-3367</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;This issue was created by maloo for sarah &amp;lt;sarah@whamcloud.com&amp;gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This issue relates to the following test suite run: &lt;a href=&quot;http://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sets/6752fdd2-bf04-11e2-88e0-52540035b04c&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;http://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sets/6752fdd2-bf04-11e2-88e0-52540035b04c&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;


