                                                                            <comments>
                            <comment id="70241" author="yujian" created="Wed, 30 Oct 2013 13:16:24 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Hi Emoly,&lt;br/&gt;
I agree with Andreas. Please update the b2_1 patch to add server version check codes. &lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="70154" author="adilger" created="Tue, 29 Oct 2013 18:25:29 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;I&apos;d like to spend as little time as possible on the old lfsck, so I think just skipping the tests is enough. &lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="70115" author="emoly.liu" created="Tue, 29 Oct 2013 15:02:45 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Yujian, I saw your comment on &lt;a href=&quot;http://review.whamcloud.com/#/c/6454&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;http://review.whamcloud.com/#/c/6454&lt;/a&gt; that &quot;lfsck test on the following combinations will fail because there is no remove_ost_objects() on servers&quot;&lt;br/&gt;
Lustre 2.1.6 client + 2.1.5 server&lt;br/&gt;
Lustre 2.1.6 client + 2.2.0 server&lt;br/&gt;
Lustre 2.1.6 client + 2.3.0 server&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Do you think we need backport the patch for these server branches or just add version check for them?&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="69495" author="yujian" created="Tue, 22 Oct 2013 04:26:39 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Lustre client build: &lt;a href=&quot;http://build.whamcloud.com/job/lustre-master/1728/&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;http://build.whamcloud.com/job/lustre-master/1728/&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br/&gt;
Lustre server build: &lt;a href=&quot;http://build.whamcloud.com/job/lustre-b2_1/219/&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;http://build.whamcloud.com/job/lustre-b2_1/219/&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The failure still occurred:&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;a href=&quot;https://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sets/7b9c0322-3ad0-11e3-8520-52540035b04c&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sets/7b9c0322-3ad0-11e3-8520-52540035b04c&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;preformatted panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;preformattedContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;rpc.sh: line 20: remove_ost_objects: command not found
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Patch &lt;a href=&quot;http://review.whamcloud.com/6454&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;http://review.whamcloud.com/6454&lt;/a&gt; needs to be updated and landed on Lustre b2_1 branch.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="69441" author="jlevi" created="Mon, 21 Oct 2013 19:51:28 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Patches landed to master.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="69440" author="adilger" created="Mon, 21 Oct 2013 19:51:15 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Emoly, Yu Jian,&lt;br/&gt;
the 6494 patch has landed to master - is this problem fixed?&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="59610" author="emoly.liu" created="Thu, 30 May 2013 06:43:06 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Similar patch for master/b24 is at &lt;a href=&quot;http://review.whamcloud.com/#change,6494&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;http://review.whamcloud.com/#change,6494&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="59409" author="emoly.liu" created="Tue, 28 May 2013 09:08:48 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;I found a problem in this test that we used 2.4 as client and 2.1 as server. I&apos;m not sure what purpose of this kind of test, but obviously some scripts in 2.4 client can&apos;t be found or interpreted in 2.1 server.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I will check if we need version check code for lfsck test.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="59339" author="emoly.liu" created="Mon, 27 May 2013 02:58:56 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://review.whamcloud.com/6454&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;http://review.whamcloud.com/6454&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="59324" author="pjones" created="Sat, 25 May 2013 14:10:23 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Emoly&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Are you able to take care of this one as you wrote the original patch?&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Thanks&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Peter&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="59323" author="yujian" created="Sat, 25 May 2013 11:32:11 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;The patch in &lt;a href=&quot;http://review.whamcloud.com/5981&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;http://review.whamcloud.com/5981&lt;/a&gt; needs to be back-ported to Lustre b2_1 branch.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
